OL,3,CEight-year-old among three injured
OL,4,Cafter car crashes into service station
OL,5,Cshop
OL,7,FThree people, including an 8-year-old
OL,8,Fchild, have been injured after a
OL,9,Fvehicle collided with a shop at an M4
OL,10,Fservice station near Cardiff.
OL,12,FThe incident happened at Cardiff Gate
OL,13,Fservices at around 11.30am on Monday
OL,14,Fmorning (25 May).
OL,16,FThree people have been taken to
OL,17,Fhospital including an 8-year-old child
OL,18,Fand a 39-year-old man, who were both
OL,19,Fpedestrians, and a 76-year-old woman,
OL,20,Fwho was driver of the vehicle.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/2
