OL,3,CEight-year-old among three injured
OL,4,Cafter car crashes into service station
OL,5,Cshop
OL,7,FSouth Wales Police say none of their
OL,8,Finjuries are believed to be life
OL,9,Fthreatening.
OL,11,FThe services remain closed with
OL,12,Femergency services still in attendance.
OL,14,FThe force says that an investigation
OL,15,Finto the incident is underway.
